{"tid":2397204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【多圖慎入】前蘇聯核試場曾引爆456顆核彈　輻射遺禍哈薩克釀百萬人悲劇","createTime":"2021-02-06T08:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T09:27:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"772cf93c96afed2af766d3cb8bf978a15ea473bf","tid":2397204,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"位於哈薩克東北部的「塞米巴拉金斯克基地」（Semipalatinsk），曾是前蘇聯時期的核武器試驗場，在1949至1989年40年間曾引爆過456顆核彈，官方估計超過40年來共有逾百萬人受輻射影響。如今多年過去，當地居民仍持續出現癌症及畸形症狀，自殺率也比一般地區高4倍。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外國媒體報道，塞米巴拉金斯克是世上碩果僅存、仍有成千上萬人居住的前核武器試驗場。前蘇聯統治時期，曾在當地進行500多次核試驗，在空中投放或在地底引爆共456顆核彈，估計多達數以萬頃土地受輻射汙染，影響人數逾百萬人。<br />\n<br />\n一直到1989年進行最後一次核試，蘇聯亦正式在1991年解體，基地也隨之關閉。但即使核試結束了，殘留輻射量仍遠高於人類生存安全標準，大量放射性物質殘留在空中及地上，嚴重影響當地人民健康，導致畸形、罹患各種癌症及患上罕見病情形頻生。<br />\n<br />\n當地孤兒院自50年代起，收到有嚴重神經系統及身體異常疾病的嬰兒數目劇增。國際廢除核武運動（International Campaign to Abolish Nuclear Weapons）成員Alicia Sanders-Zakre表示，蘇聯多次核試已造成多人死亡，並衍生出殘留核輻射問題，禍延數代，世世代代也飽受疾病摧殘。<br />\n<br />\n當地人罹患血癌、肺癌、乳癌、食道癌、胃癌及甲狀腺癌數量，是其他地區的幾倍，甚至有指自殺率高於全國平均4倍以上。<br />\n<br />\n而即使輻射影響深遠，有報道卻指出政府從未告知人民生活在輻射區的知識，仍未提供適當援助，甚至傳出鼓勵人民喝伏特加抗輻射，並縱容當地畜牧者將含輻射的肉類銷售至鄰近地區，令人當地居民是被當成白老鼠進行實驗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2872382/nuclear_thumb_20210205_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2872382%2Fnuclear_thumb_20210205_S_1024.jpg&h=a24ff19a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2872382/AFP20110828_442521_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2872382%2FAFP20110828_442521_1024_1024.jpg&h=4a3502b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2872382/12_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2872382%2F12_1024.jpg&h=d6da957f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2872382/03_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2872382%2F03_1024.jpg&h=9643ad8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2872382/11_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2872382%2F11_1024.jpg&h=6b10f9b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2872382/05_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2872382%2F05_1024.jpg&h=36a67251&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b5648aee5eb5536acdb65891cfc78456475e7f8","tid":2397204,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:41:34.000Z","msg":"碩果僅存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d02ff01a59ad220748886787ccd9f81359b7d96","tid":2397204,"uid":356233,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"7b5648aee5eb5536acdb65891cfc78456475e7f8","tid":2397204,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:41:34.000Z","msg":"碩果僅存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"笑乜? 生活係香港係一件好幸福既事"},{"pid":"2001c5fa3f7561c428e1eb6ad95610d742f1b91b","tid":2397204,"uid":66324,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7d02ff01a59ad220748886787ccd9f81359b7d96","tid":2397204,"uid":356233,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"7b5648aee5eb5536acdb65891cfc78456475e7f8","tid":2397204,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:41:34.000Z","msg":"碩果僅存<img src=\"/assets/faces